{
  "type": "buff",
  "name": "KOUSOKU (SPEED RANK)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Characters that are <em>helpless, paralyzed, immobilized, grappled</em> or <em>pinned</em> are automatically reduced to speed rank 0. You take a -1 Speed Rank penalty while wearing medium armor, or a -3 penalty while wearing heavy armor.</p><p><strong>Dodge:</strong> The dodge bonus applies to Defense and Reflex saves, and does not function if you are denied your Dexterity bonus to Defense.</p><p><strong>Hide:</strong> This hide bonus applies only in situations where fast movement would help.</p><p><strong>Kawarimi Defense:</strong> If you attack an opponent while having this quality, they cannot use <em>defensive maneuvers</em> or <em>avoiding an attack</em> type actions against the attack unless they are moving at the specified speed rank.</p><p><strong>Extra Attacks:</strong> You can make additional attacks during a Full Attack, using your highest attack bonus -5. At Speed Rank 7 the -5 penalty is removed. At Speed Rank 10, you gain a second extra attack, at your highest attack bonus -5.</p><table><caption>Table 1-5: Speed Ranks</caption><thead><tr><th>Speed Rank</th><th>Jump</th><th>Dodge</th><th>Attack</th><th>Speed</th><th>Hide</th><th>Kawarimi Defense</th><th>Extra Attacks *</th><th>Cost</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>+2</td><td>+1</td><td>-</td><td>+10ft</td><td>+1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>1 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>+3</td><td>+2</td><td>+1</td><td>+15ft</td><td>+2</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>2 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>+4</td><td>+3</td><td>+1</td><td>+20ft</td><td>+3</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>3 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>+5</td><td>+4</td><td>+2</td><td>+25ft</td><td>+4</td><td>1</td><td>-</td><td>4 / 5 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>+6</td><td>+5</td><td>+2</td><td>+30ft</td><td>+5</td><td>2</td><td>-</td><td>1 / round</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>+7</td><td>+6</td><td>+3</td><td>+35ft</td><td>+6</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>3 / 2 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>+8</td><td>+7</td><td>+3</td><td>+40ft</td><td>+7</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>2 / round</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>+9</td><td>+8</td><td>+4</td><td>+45ft</td><td>+8</td><td>4</td><td>1</td><td>5 / 2 rounds</td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td>+10</td><td>+9</td><td>+4</td><td>+50ft</td><td>+9</td><td>5</td><td>1</td><td>3 / round</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>+10</td><td>+10</td><td>+5</td><td>+60ft</td><td>+10</td><td>6</td><td>2</td><td>5 / round</td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "instructions": ""
    },
